{"tid":2135258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應被警通緝消息　黃台仰：正正揭示行使國安法追溯權","createTime":"2020-08-01T09:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T10:23:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76bd4c75a5e83a9a862d8b79bff660aefde21402","tid":2135258,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541245-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541245-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PshAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=6a9b81c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541245-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1ac5ad48\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541245-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n身在海外的本土民主前線前召集人黃台仰，在社交網頁回應有關他被香港警方通緝的消息。<br />\n<br />\n黃台仰說，去年5月他已宣布不再主張香港獨立，而且自從《港區國安法》生效之後，他亦再沒有與被指是「外國勢力」的政治人物談及任何關於港獨的事情，因此指他煽動分裂國家和勾結外國勢力的唯一理據，應該是基於他在國安法生效前進行的活動，這正正揭示特區政府行使《港區國安法》的追溯權力。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方正通緝6名在海外的港人，包括黃台仰、前香港眾志常委羅冠聰、前香港獨立聯盟召集人陳家駒、學生動源前成員劉康、英國駐港總領事館前職員鄭文傑、海外港人組織「香港民主委員會」總監朱牧民。他們分別涉嫌煽動分裂國家、勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全。"},{"pid":"c090096ed9e194745be11a312f22859944cad0cb","tid":2135258,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b00ee748aa334dd8bac910cc86e0beccd66b2dce","tid":2135258,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"毅進警不嬲係害蟲"},{"pid":"5cf3882f2fc6a3c035c57d61b399325f01f9b93e","tid":2135258,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QOYBph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QOYBph.jpg&h=7ef35f25&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}